posting_body: ['Ask us about our renovations!', 'Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Come home to a resort-inspired apartment community in Plantation, FL.', 'Our apartments offer an oasis with beautiful lake views and great amenities in studio, one bedroom, two bedroom, and even three bedroom layouts.', 'You will find the perfect selection of modern floor plans with open-concept layouts.', 'Residents love the convenience of a washer and dryer in their apartment home as well as additional storage availability!', 'Amenities:', '-Picnic & Barbecue Areas', '-Clubhouse', '-Frost-free Fridge w/ Icemaker', '-Screen Patio and Balcony', '-Vaulted Ceilings', '-Industrial-sized Fitness Center', '-Exterior Storage', '-Two Resort-style Swimming Pools', '-Dishwasher', '-Business Center & Resident Lounge', '-Conference Room', '-Tennis & Basketball Courts', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
